prompts.prompt: Design a responsive landing page for a tech/business-related startup with a sleek dark mode. The page should feature a navigation bar with links to 'Home,' 'About Us,' and 'Contact Us.' The homepage should prominently display 'Coming Soon' text. The design should be suitable for a tech-savvy audience and convey a professional, modern, and forward-looking image. Please ensure it looks great in both desktop and mobile views."
